To Create a super user or admin panel we have to run this command:-

Step 1 :- First Get In The Change Directory :- cd myproject

Step 2 :- To connect Data base we have to run These command
                First :- python manage.py makemigrations
                Second :- python manage.py migrate

Run Command In Your My Project Directory :-python manage.py createsuperuser

NOTE-> 
ALWAYS CHANGE YOUR PROJECT NAME in settings.py in project folder
in this line
WSGI_APPLICATION = 'myproject.wsgi.application'

TO this Eg:-
WSGI_APPLICATION = 'Tridev.wsgi.application'


